<section id="troubleshooting-first-steps">
<title>Troubleshooting First Steps</title>
<p><b>Build fails?</b></p>
<ol>
  <li>Check DITA-OT installation (<codeph>dita --version</codeph>)</li>
  <li>Verify Java version (<codeph>java -version</codeph> → 17+)</li>
  <li>Review error message for specific issue</li>
  <li>Check <xref href="../appendices/architecture-diagram.dita">Architecture Diagram</xref> to identify stage</li>
</ol>
<p><b>Content not appearing?</b></p>
<ol>
  <li>Check DITAVAL filtering (conditional processing)</li>
  <li>Verify topic is referenced in map</li>
  <li>Check chunking settings</li>
  <li>Examine temp files in work directory</li>
</ol>
<p><b>HTML looks wrong?</b></p>
<ol>
  <li>Verify CSS path in build properties</li>
  <li>Check XSLT overrides are installed</li>
  <li>Clear browser cache</li>
  <li>Review generated HTML source</li>
</ol>
<p><b>Need more help?</b></p>
<ul>
  <li><xref href="../part08-customize/xslt-customization-tutorial.dita">Troubleshooting section</xref></li>
  <li><xref href="../part07-develop/dita-ot-developer-handbook.dita">Debugging playbook</xref></li>
</ul>
</section>
